source.name: Information Bridge Data Service
source.description: Contains bibliographic data for Department of Energy (DOE) research report literature available in full-text online in the DOE Information Bridge.  Default request returns first one hundred records.  See Technical Documentation for instructions on obtaining additional records.  This data service allows the downloading of bibliographic records in formats that can be used to load the records into other databases or search tools.  To search the DOE Information Bridge, use the Agency Program Page below.
